  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary objective of this web-based, cross-sectional study is to assess and compare the
      ability to sleep, work or go to school, and to participate in leisure activities among
      subjects who are receiving Xolair treatment and subjects who were eligible to receive Xolair,
      but instead have been using Advair for at least 1 year.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
