    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Have asthma and allergies

          -  Currently taking Xolair速 or Advair速

          -  Started Xolair速 treatment within the last 4 to 12 months OR have been taking Advair速
             for at least 12 months

          -  Between 18 and 55 years of age

          -  A non-smoker for at least 6 months

          -  Have internet access
      </textblock>
